#: ../custom_search.rst:31
msgid ""
"We use the new catalog indexes to provide the data for the widgets and "
"search the results. For other use-cases we could also use either the "
"built-in vocabularies (https://pypi.org/project/plone.app.vocabularies) "
"or create custom vocabularies for this."
msgstr ""
"Usaremos el nuevo índice de catálogo para proveer la data de los widgets y "
"buscar los resultados. Para otros casos de uso podremos usar entre los "
"vocabularios integrados (https://pypi.org/project/plone.app.vocabularies) o "
"crear vocabularios personalizados para este."

#: ../custom_search.rst:33
msgid ""
